    Scope and Contents
CHRIST EPISCOPAL CHURCH 
Leinicke, member of Christ Episcopal Church in Springfield, discusses changes in the services, form of church government, priests and bishops, conflicts between high and low Episcopal churches, election of women, and the Prayer Book. She also talks about her participation in the church, women's organizations, couples groups, election to the Synod, and membership in other  governing bodies in the church and the Diocese. 2 tapes, 180 mins., 45 pp. 
Interview by Sandra Britz Armbruster, 1981 
